{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-10535/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-10535"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:05:35"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman closes her eyes in frustration."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-10535","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-10535"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1/a42fb495-1ffe-49a0-abea-444ec405ec96","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:34:47.065Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Alma asks Reynolds whether he’ll make the Princess’s wedding gown, what she obviously has in mind is the fact that Reynolds hasn’t proposed to <em>her</em>. Reynolds doesn’t plan on marrying the Princess, of course, but for Alma, this desire is sublimated into the act of making the wedding dress.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:636.8577981651372,227.62184633027508,571.2514334862387,277.79529816513764"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1/166c25bf-17e9-4fbe-9674-3631128a4290","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:35:04.948Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma says, “Let me serve you,” offering to bring out the food she has prepared for their dinner after he seems angry with her. When she feels he is displeased, she reverts to a subservient position, hoping that will soothe him. This is also a nod to their first meeting, where she was his waitress. She cannot escape her role from their first meeting and become his true equal.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10535/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:640.8643922018347,545.7052752293577,567.1014908256883,256.5797018348625"}}}]}]}]}